{"tid":1448622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母死黑警 還眼啊！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:24.000Z","uid":175493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2571d9adb783226d7faa42e79b9b5a0940d7ab9e","tid":1448622,"uid":175493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=6ec7a03c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=b5fc4d71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"b8800cd09e956dea0d7ffa44e65b403edc12068b","tid":1448622,"uid":175493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9243846f535e72116e39dce6a7b5a62823831a46","tid":1448622,"uid":175493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9eec3625a999b1fc17fdc2922f0765b50997088a","tid":1448622,"uid":175493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"062adcf245078ed506343b8ba40a554705fdf8d7","tid":1448622,"uid":175493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"推啊<img sr